headline: A Look Back at Travel and Vacation Providers Stocks’ Q2 Earnings: Royal Caribbean (NYSE:RCL) Vs The Rest Of The Pack
summary: As the Q2 earnings season comes to a close, it’s time to take stock of this quarter’s best and worst performers in the travel and vacation providers industry, including Royal Caribbean (NYSE:RCL) and its peers.
